e: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/a59e9/camera6.webp 192w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/0ca9f/camera6.webp 384w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/dc9b9/camera6.webp 768w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/e2c2f/camera6.webp 1152w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/f3efb/camera6.webp 1536w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/02082/camera6.webp 4624w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/150b2/camera6.jpg 192w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/6985d/camera6.jpg 384w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/19de6/camera6.jpg 768w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/4472f/camera6.jpg 1152w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/d58d1/camera6.jpg 1536w,\n/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/2faad/camera6.jpg 4624w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/666527bb6ddbf595bba7bd56fdf25d9a/19de6/camera6.jpg\"\n            alt=\"5\"\n            title=\"5\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>파티션 설정시, 기존에있는 windows를 없애기 위해 something else 항목을 선택하여 직접 파티션을 설정해줘야 합니다. 필요한 파티션의 종류는 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>efi 파티션</strong><br>\n없으면 부팅이 안됩니다. 꼭 설정을해야 하며, 용량은 500MB 내외로, primary 디스크로 설정하면 됩니다.</li>\n<li><strong>swap 파티션</strong><br>\n메모리와 디스크간의 스왑을 위해 설정하며, 필수는 아니지만 설정하면 좋습니다. 저는 SSD 용량이 넉넉하여 4GB로 설정했습니다.</li>\n<li><strong>ext4 / 파티션</strong><br>\n커널, root등 실제 리눅스에 필요한 파일들이 설치되는 파티션입니다. 경로는 / 로 설정하면 되고, 용량은 나머지 전부를 사용했습니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"설치-완료\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EC%99%84%EB%A3%8C\" aria-label=\"설치 완료 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>설치 완료</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8dba9b7a57b183e39f9f701112dba36f/e2f49/Screenshot1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8dba9b7a57b183e39f9f701112dba36f/a59e9/Screenshot1.webp 192w,\n/static/8dba9b7a57b183e39f9f701112dba36f/0ca9f/Screenshot1.webp 384w,\n/static/8dba9b7a57b183e39f9f701112dba36f/dc9b9/Screenshot1.webp 768w,\n/static/8dba9b7a57b183e39f9f701112dba36f/e2c2f/Screenshot1.webp 1152w,\n/static/8dba9b7a57b183e39f9f701112dba36f/1ea9b/Screenshot1.webp 1366w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8dba9b7a57b183e39f9f701112dba36f/3b721/Screenshot1.png 192w,\n/static/8dba9b7a57b183e39f9f701112dba36f/66595/Screenshot1.png 